s3077: King Xiang, first year. The feudal lords established the king.
s3078: 9. Qi led us to attack Jin disorder, reached Gao Liang and returned.
s3079: 35. Summer, assembled feudal lords at Kui Qiu. The Son of Heaven sent Steward Kong to grant the sacrificial meat, commanded not to bow.
s3080: 26. The duke died, established Xi Qi, Li Ke killed him. And Zhuo Zi. Established Yi Wu.
s3081: 9. Yi Wu sent Xi Rui to bribe, sought to enter.
s3083: 31. The duke died, not yet buried, Qi Huan assembled at Kui Qiu.
